Create a ScrollView, set its size, inner container size, and direction:

```typescript
const sv = new ccui.ScrollView();
sv.setSize(cc.size(300, 400));
sv.setInnerContainerSize(cc.size(300, 1200));
sv.setDirection(ccui.ScrollView.DIR_VERTICAL);
sv.setBounceEnabled(true);
sv.setScrollBarEnabled(true);
sv.setPosition(50, 50);
this.addChild(sv);
```

The inner container size must be >= the ScrollView size. Add children to the inner container: `sv.getInnerContainer().addChild(child)`.

